# Project-wide workaround for the webapp build which might fail due to JavaScript heap memory leaks.
# `node-options` is still honoured by pnpm 11 as a Node-level setting. The pnpm-specific install
# settings (shamefullyHoist, publicHoistPattern, preferFrozenLockfile, enablePrePostScripts, allowBuilds)
# moved to pnpm-workspace.yaml.
node-options=--max-old-space-size=6144
